OL,5, The government's chief scientific      
OL,6, adviser Sir Patrick Vallance says his  
OL,7, job is "not to sugarcoat" reality when 
OL,8, speaking to the PM about Covid.        
OL,10,FHe said he had to give Boris Johnson   
OL,11,Fand MPs the evidence - not worrying    
OL,12,Fwhether they would like it.            
OL,14,FIn a BBC Radio 4 interview, he also    
OL,15,Fsaid "you've got to go sooner than you 
OL,16,Fwant" when it comes to taking action.  
OL,18,FHe was speaking before a report said   
OL,19,Fthe UK's early Covid response was one  
OL,20,Fof the worst public health failures.   
